#. RST means "Rapid Storage Technology". Don't translate it.
#: ../ubiquity.templates:251001
msgid "Turn off RST"
msgstr "關閉 Rapid Storage Technology (RST)"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:252001
msgid ""
"This computer uses Intel RST (Rapid Storage Technology). You need to turn "
"off RST before installing Linux Mint. For instructions, open this page on a "
"phone or other device: <a href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/rst\">help.ubuntu."
"com/rst</a>"
msgstr ""
"本電腦使用 Intel RST (Rapid Storage Technology) 技術。必須關閉 RST 才能安裝 "
"Linux Mint。請在手機或其他裝置打開此網頁，以取得設定指引：<a href=\"https://"
"help.ubuntu.com/rst\">help.ubuntu.com/rst</a>"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:253001
msgid "Turn off BitLocker"
msgstr "關閉 BitLocker"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:254001
msgid ""
"This computer uses Windows BitLocker encryption. You need to turn off "
"BitLocker in Windows before installing Linux Mint. For instructions, open "
"this page on a phone or other device: <a href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/"
"bitlocker\">help.ubuntu.com/bitlocker</a>"
msgstr ""
"本電腦使用 Windows BitLocker 加密技術。必須在 Windows 關閉 BitLocker 才能安"
"裝 Linux Mint。請在手機或其他裝置打開此網頁，以取得設定指引：<a "
"href=\"https://help.ubuntu.com/bitlocker\">help.ubuntu.com/bitlocker</a>"

