"<span foreground=\"darkred\">Warning:</span> This will delete all your "
"${CURDISTRO} programs, documents, photos, music, and any other files."
msgstr ""
"<span foreground=\"darkred\">警告：</span>這會刪除您所有的 ${CURDISTRO} 程"
