msgstr "重新安裝 ${CURDISTRO}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:294001
msgid ""
"Documents, music, and other personal files will be kept. Installed software "
"and system-wide settings will be cleared."
msgstr ""
"您的文件、音樂與其他的個人檔案將被保留。安裝的軟體與系統全域設定則會被清除。"

